{"tid":1880604,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"父母被困鑽石公主號　【森美】擔心兩老安全","createTime":"2020-02-15T03:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T03:43:42.000Z","uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9502a6c00529c06d80b0d9619210a1d979be13","tid":1880604,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1701559/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E6%BB%AF%E7%95%99%E6%A8%AA%E6%BF%B1-%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E8%A2%AB%E5%9B%B0%E9%91%BD%E7%9F%B3%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB%E8%99%9F-%E6%A3%AE%E7%BE%8E%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83%E5%85%A9%E8%80%81%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1701559%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582-%25E6%25BB%25AF%25E7%2595%2599%25E6%25A8%25AA%25E6%25BF%25B1-%25E7%2588%25B6%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%259B%25B0%25E9%2591%25BD%25E7%259F%25B3%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%2599%259F-%25E6%25A3%25AE%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2593%2594%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2585%25A9%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=fe8e8a63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1701559%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582-%25E6%25BB%25AF%25E7%2595%2599%25E6%25A8%25AA%25E6%25BF%25B1-%25E7%2588%25B6%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%259B%25B0%25E9%2591%25BD%25E7%259F%25B3%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%2599%259F-%25E6%25A3%25AE%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2593%2594%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2585%25A9%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8&h=dbeef628\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1701559/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E6%BB%AF%E7%95%99%E6%A8%AA%E6%BF%B1-%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E8%A2%AB%E5%9B%B0%E9%91%BD%E7%9F%B3%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB%E8%99%9F-%E6%A3%AE%E7%BE%8E%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83%E5%85%A9%E8%80%81%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8</a><br />\n森美、陳貝兒及林溥來等錄影《全民開講齊抗疫》，森美解釋手指因噴上酒精消毒搓手液而乾裂，故戴上手套保護，減少手指接觸酒精的機會。他又指最擔心父母的安全，皆因兩老正身處停泊在橫濱的「鑽石公主號郵輪」上。他說：「他們是初一登船，初頭以為沒事，還可以自由活動，豈料船上愈來愈多人發燒及確診新型肺炎，大家都要入房隔離，他們又是住在冇窗的低層房間，這些天只靠短訊及照片每日報告情況，幸好他們都沒有出現病徵，而確診的港人亦非父母的同行朋友。」<br />\n<br />\n左起：林溥來、陳貝兒及森美錄影《全民開講齊抗疫》。<br />\n左起：林溥來、陳貝兒及森美錄影《全民開講齊抗疫》。<br />\n森美透露擔心被困在鑽石公主號的父母。<br />\n森美透露擔心被困在鑽石公主號的父母。<br />\n森美表示如無意外，父母將於下周三完成14日隔離，船上的補給食物、口罩及酒精等亦充足，只是未能外出活動，其間只曾獲准「放風」十多分鐘。他說：「父母原本沒告訴我是在該郵輪，怕我擔心，阿哥講我才知道，我有叮囑他們在房內多做運動，增強抵抗力，希望他們能盡快回港。（有人要求政府包機接船上港人回港？）船上有數百個港人，大家都有不同要求，有人想離船隔離，有人想政府幫他們回港，我覺得只要父母安全，盡快離開郵輪，在哪裡隔離也可以。」"},{"pid":"7f2526416ab1aa3aca6dba208657dd9f897eb792","tid":1880604,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e74106ac5a8e88ac398a936665a589b743a472","tid":1880604,"uid":341040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:39:40.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"92d44ac9e2f27c5bf14f41cab86d4af27ec67119","tid":1880604,"uid":240608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:43:42.000Z","msg":"好高危<br />\n年紀大，又無支援<br />\n<br />\n一陣返到香港 無病徵惹埋森美點算"}]}